data.meta_description: Dielman Edward Kolb (Culp) was born on January 28, 1648 in Wolfsheim, Baden-Wuerttemberg, Germany, son of Heinrich :Henry" Jacob Kolb and Marie Barbara Feltz. He was married in the year 1653 in Germany to Agnes Hendricks Schumacher He was married in the year 1670 in Wolfsheim, Hessen, Germany to Agnes Hendricks Schumacher He was married in the year 1679 to Agnes Hendricks Schumacher He was married in Germany to Agnes Hendricks Schumacher, they had 13 children. He died on December 13, 1711 in Mannheim, Mannheimer Stadtkreis, Baden-Württemberg, Germany. This information is part of Family tree Cromer/Russell/Buck/Pratt by Elizabeth Cromer on Genealogy Online.
